definition: Yu county in Zhangjiakou 張家口|张家口[Zhang1 jia1 kou3], Hebei

sentences.english: I went there two times, one is in summer, and the other is in winter.
sentences.chinese: 我分別在夏天和冬天兩次走進蔚縣。

sentences.english: Yuxian formerly paper -cut window, a Chinese folk paper -cut of the fine arts.
sentences.chinese: 蔚縣剪紙原名窗花，屬中國民間剪紙藝術中的精品。

sentences.english: Wei County Paper-cut, originally called window decoration, is the artistic treasure of Chinese folk Paper-cut.
sentences.chinese: 蔚縣剪紙原名窗花，屬中國民間剪紙藝術中的精品。
